Update 0.5.1 - 22/01/2025
Mojave Mo' Problems Changelog 0.5.1

Save Safe
- Tweaked some ini settings for a handful of mods. This is primarily to reintroduce things like Fo3's Repair system as well as certain abilities tied to special perks.
- Tweaked the sounds for certain weapon types so they no longer sound off.
- Added an optional section for NVR. If you'd like to enable NVR< enable all of the mods in this section.
- Removed redundant downloads.
- Added aWRP > https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/82558
